![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578270651123-RJU2BE0FZ8YF5GHDGDNG/Episode90.jpg?format=original)

WOW! What a week it has been in comic book media news! From Marvel revealing a litany of new shows and properties at D23, to Joker becoming the first R Rated DC film of all  time, and we can’t forget the family court drama that is Sony and Disney wrestling over Spider-Man. We thought we’d take our time this week and give each of these announcements some breathing room as we sift through the madness is Marvel in a post-Spider-Man/ D23 world while exploring some of the new and exciting directions the MCU seems to be going with interesting new characters.

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience, and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
